{"tid":1001151,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Computer Vision撚］有冇人玩過COCO object recognition / keypoint 比賽","createTime":"2019-01-30T02:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T10:40:32.000Z","uid":77368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff71074fa8d72bd4482158e4739362c885d0413","tid":1001151,"uid":77368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:27:30.000Z","msg":"純粹想知究竟有幾多連登巴打對computer vision 係有興趣/從事相關研究工作,次撚次問都冇咩人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果知道有人參加呢一類嘅比賽都出下聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸果啲 AI challenger 都得㗎，到底要幾多processing power 先做到,之前聽過吓話要用十幾部有Tesla gpu 嘅電腦train成個禮拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話推AI , 但就成日講 algorithm trading , 但computer vision 就冇人理，之前商湯唔係話有整無人車㗎咩,究竟有冇中大巴打做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實自己真係好廢,但真心想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ef041d4e94327c7c3e94d702667c2068f5a5ae","tid":1001151,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"商湯果班係prof親生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952833502d103951748a4cd02ffacddf5c306aa8","tid":1001151,"uid":77368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60ef041d4e94327c7c3e94d702667c2068f5a5ae","tid":1001151,"uid":121095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"商湯果班係prof親生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"咁都係想睇下有冇人攪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}